OL,3,CItalian officials jailed over 2018
OL,4,CGenoa bridge collapse
OL,6,FThe former boss of an Italian motorway
OL,7,Foperator has been jailed for 12 years
OL,8,Fover the collapse of a bridge in Genoa
OL,9,Fthat killed 43 people nearly eight
OL,10,Fyears ago.
OL,12,FAn Italian court on Thursday convicted
OL,13,Fformer CEO of Autostrade per l'Italia
OL,14,FGiovanni Castellucci and other
OL,15,Fofficials, after a series of trials
OL,16,Fover four years and four hours of
OL,17,Fdeliberations.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
