OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1784285298
OL,3,CItalian officials jailed over 2018
OL,4,CGenoa bridge collapse
OL,6,FHe was among dozens of defendants
OL,7,Fconvicted in the collapse that
OL,8,Frevealed serious lapses in the
OL,9,Fmaintenance of Italian infrastructure.
OL,11,FOn the morning of August 14, 2018, a
OL,12,F200-metre (650-foot) section of
OL,13,FGenoa's Morandi highway bridge gave
OL,14,Fway during a rainstorm, sending dozens
OL,15,Fof vehicles plunging to the ground.
OL,17,FThe incident happened on one of
OL,18,FItaly's busiest travel days, as
OL,19,Fmillions headed out for the
OL,20,Ftraditional Ferragosto holiday that
OL,21,Fmarks the peak summer holiday season.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1784285298
OL,3,CItalian officials jailed over 2018
OL,4,CGenoa bridge collapse
OL,6,FThe 57 defendants include former
OL,7,Fexecutives of highway operator
OL,8,FAutostrade per L'Italia, experts from
OL,9,Fits engineering company SPEA and
OL,10,Fformer officials from Italy's
OL,11,FInfrastructure and Transport Ministry.
OL,13,FMost face charges, including negligent
OL,14,Fdisaster and multiple counts of
OL,15,Fmanslaughter stemming from alleged
OL,16,Ffailures to maintain the bridge, which
OL,17,Fwas part of a main route linking
OL,18,Fnorthern Italy with the French Riviera.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1784285298
OL,3,CItalian officials jailed over 2018
OL,4,CGenoa bridge collapse
OL,6,FProsecutors argued that years of
OL,7,Fmaintenance neglect led to the
OL,8,Fcollapse, and demanded combined
OL,9,Fsentences totaling nearly 400 years
OL,10,Ffor all of the defendants. The
OL,11,Fdefendants deny wrongdoing and say the
OL,12,Ffault was caused by a construction
OL,13,Fdefect.
OL,15,FThe verdicts and sentencing will cap a
OL,16,Ftrial that spanned more than 280
OL,17,Fhearings over four years.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
