OL,3,CItalian officials jailed over 2018
OL,4,CGenoa bridge collapse
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,F"I think it is important that
OL,12,Fresponsibility extends beyond those at
OL,13,Fthe top. Autostrade, SPEA and the
OL,14,FTransport Ministry all had roles to
OL,15,Fplay. I hope the state's
OL,16,Fresponsibility also emerges clearly,"
OL,17,FEgle Possetti, who heads a committee
OL,18,Fto preserve the memory of the bridge
OL,19,Fvictims, told reporters outside the
OL,20,Fcourthouse.
OL,26,@sD@AOUxD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
