PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1784285298
OL,3,CItalian officials jailed over 2018
OL,4,CGenoa bridge collapse
OL,6,F"I lost my sister, her two children,
OL,7,Fmy brother-in-law and even their
OL,8,Flittle dog. That's where my
OL,9,Fdetermination comes from ` to make
OL,10,Fsure they receive justice and that
OL,11,Ftheir deaths were not in vain," she
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,F"Our expectation is to feel our pain
OL,15,Frecognised ... and to have it
OL,16,Facknowledged that this did not happen
OL,17,Fby chance, but because of serious
OL,18,Ffailures in maintenance," said
OL,19,FRaffaele Caruso, one of the lawyers
OL,20,Frepresenting victims.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@_O]vD@AOUzD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
