OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1784285298
OL,3,CItalian officials jailed over 2018
OL,4,CGenoa bridge collapse
OL,6,FConsidered an engineering marvel when
OL,7,Fit opened in 1967, the Morandi
OL,8,Ffeatured three A-shaped concrete
OL,9,Fpylons and concrete-encased stay
OL,10,Fcables.
OL,12,FA new bridge designed by Genoa-born
OL,13,FItalian architect Renzo Piano opened
OL,14,Fin 2020, spanning a memorial to the
OL,15,Fvictims of the Morandi Bridge collapse.
OL,17,FCaruso, who represents the family
OL,18,Fmembers of three victims, said that
OL,19,Fthe trial showed that warning signs
OL,20,Fabout defects in the pylon that
OL,21,Fcollapsed had existed for decades.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30908
