CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1784285298
OL,3,CItalian officials jailed over 2018
OL,4,CGenoa bridge collapse
OL,6,F"From 1993 onward, the problem was
OL,7,Fknown," Caruso said.
OL,9,F"We had three identical pylons. Two
OL,10,Fhad already shown the same defect, and
OL,11,Fno one seriously asked whether the
OL,12,Fthird one had it as well."
OL,14,FThe current Autostrade chief
OL,15,Fexecutive, Arrigo Giana, issued a
OL,16,Fpublic apology Thursday in an open
OL,17,Fletter published in major Italian
OL,18,Fdailies.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
