CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1784285298
OL,3,CItalian officials jailed over 2018
OL,4,CGenoa bridge collapse
OL,6,F"The actions and decisions of some
OL,7,Fpeople left indelible scars,'' said
OL,8,FGiana, who joined Autostrade as CEO
OL,9,Flast year. "Offering today the apology
OL,10,Fthat was not made then is, for us, a
OL,11,Fmoral imperative that goes beyond
OL,12,Festablishing legal responsibility and
OL,13,Fthe course of justice toward the
OL,14,Ftruth."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@LOUvD@GO]
